commit.message:
Add S3 bucket validation to s3 mv

When the --validate-same-s3-paths parameter is used
or the env var AWS_CLI_S3_MV_VALIDATE_SAME_S3_PATHS
is set to true, the s3 mv command will resolve
underlying bucket names of source and destination
S3 URIs and validate that an object is not being
moved onto itself.
